Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\N Just Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.23,0:00:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.77,0:00:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.88,0:00:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.09,0:00:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.89,0:00:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.17,0:01:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.61,0:01:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.28,0:01:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.92,0:01:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民衛星派來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.00,0:01:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五部鋼彈的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.00,0:01:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是衛星反抗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.34,0:01:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈藏身在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯合軍的機動戰士部隊內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.78,0:01:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以OZ為攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展開了各種作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.28,0:01:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.09,0:01:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ終於踏上歷史的表面舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.66,0:01:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,統帥特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以精銳的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.39,0:01:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行了消滅聯合軍的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.83,0:01:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被派來地球的機動戰士和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.03,0:02:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ的戰鬥令大地震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.54,0:02:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八話\N[暗殺特列斯]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用紅外線探測的爆炸裝置嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.65,0:02:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管，我要追那傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.17,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在特列斯的股掌之中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被玩弄了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徹底…輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.81,0:03:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今，我們追特列斯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在追還趕得上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.75,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太魯莽了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別阻止我!   你想退縮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的作戰本來應該是拯救地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣，敵人比較有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也講得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有沒死的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.71,0:03:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，離開這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!逃呀!會沒命啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做甚麼呀!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯特尉正指揮佔領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還繼續抵抗\N的陸遜布克總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.57,0:04:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給他就不會錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣處置新愛德華的鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那交給妳去辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.58,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這基地已經完全佔領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請批準出擊前往新愛德華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,批準出擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無必要出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們只要啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新愛德華飛彈的自爆裝置就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自爆裝置?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.09,0:05:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你們那裡應該能遙遠控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.36,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然利害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.53,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了破壞機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就炸毀一個基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.41,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼簡單的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前的聯合做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼混亂是甚麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.82,0:05:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要求著陸的飛機源源不絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.05,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是從新愛德華\N逃出來的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.36,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為鋼彈出現也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣慌忙逃生並不尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉少校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接收到OZ的通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新愛德華基地的飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.10,0:06:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想把鋼彈和基地一起炸毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即著陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這沙漠應該能緊急降落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統鎖定完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自爆裝置準備開動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體疏散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重覆，自爆裝置準備開動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣，鋼彈也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.23,0:06:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還清醒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新愛德華還有你們的同伴和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受了傷的士兵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.61,0:06:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就會變成名留青史的戰士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瘋狂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會當那是稱讚我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前聯合軍少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喪心病狂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自爆裝置最終安全鎖解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離爆炸還有900秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉少校，妳在做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統被鎖死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡已經無計可施!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那基地距離毀滅還有10分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們想消滅他們也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有一個\N強到不能消滅的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的駕駛員我很有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我設法想和他再見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!別再要我照顧你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友受了打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛!你聽到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我講!希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.58,0:07:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛?那傢伙的名字嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.85,0:07:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那基地的大型飛彈自爆裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在被啟動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ為了消滅你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.53,0:08:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想把你們和那基地一起炸毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,証實了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.66,0:08:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新愛德華基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏有47支大型飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果全部爆炸的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半徑300公里內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間就會化為灰燼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.67,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑!快逃吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離爆炸不夠10分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能去到300公里外!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能逃離那裡吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我有個不情之請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止爆炸!希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!叫希洛的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.73,0:08:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想自己逃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，他不是逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛彈基地確認，現在衝進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想做甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.98,0:08:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了，我就靠你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作戰出錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我不能就此死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝有自爆裝置的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大支的304號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.80,0:09:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這系統利用304號的爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誘爆其他的飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你快點去304號的控制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，能使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確保兩部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑道很快就能使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.09,0:10:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做沒用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.36,0:10:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，請你預先令另一部能起飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的燃料已所餘無幾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.83,0:10:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以為他會成功啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛先生啊，拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功率10%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他會做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.55,0:10:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!爆炸系統\N一點也沒停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉少校!我始終不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.58,0:10:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那基地裡有人能阻止爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.42,0:10:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，誰也不會相信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.76,0:10:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認識到敢於停止爆炸裝置的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.00,0:10:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛‧唯令我覺得很自豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.99,0:11:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何，你很厲害，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恥的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.03,0:11:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的…錯誤!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，處置鋼彈\N一事我失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.58,0:11:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.52,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳究竟想用甚麼辦法\N消滅鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開動新愛德華基地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛彈自爆裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他們和基地一起炸毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.26,0:11:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被鋼彈拆除了自爆裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸被阻止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈幫了我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球的空間有限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.31,0:12:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可胡亂污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類是渺小的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他方法也能消滅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以用那種方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.45,0:12:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今次要多謝他們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，蕾蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.02,0:12:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也再向OZ學習一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向OZ…學習?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使受到這麼猛烈的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不肯投降嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.94,0:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴高‧奧尼爾準將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頑強的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我希望\N他是個可憎的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.78,0:12:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則，傑克斯不會狠起心腸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.09,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為聯合總部\N那麼容易陷落嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.29,0:13:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這基地我不會讓OZ接近一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這基地的守衛的確完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，如果使用它的人有缺點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.64,0:13:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那城堡遲早也會陷落吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯‧馬吉斯!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.35,0:13:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯合時代你對我的戒心特別強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想那就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.69,0:13:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是時代!\N是戰爭令我那樣做的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.26,0:13:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊撤古王國不是我的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.53,0:13:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是聯合整體的意思!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤古王國沒有意思反抗聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻展開攻擊把她滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時，很多國家反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.67,0:13:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球圈統一聯合擴張軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說撤古王國是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.01,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消滅對鄰近各國有影響的王族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能收殺一儆百之效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.89,0:14:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你自己就親自指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米利亞.匹斯克拉福特!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死去的米利亞.匹斯克拉福特啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向OZ學習?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.69,0:14:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不了解特列斯大人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,505補給部隊的兩部運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要求和本艦接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,識別訊號呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我軍的艾亞利玆運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，批準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是 [碧克斯]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,批準接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩部運輸機屬於哪個基地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新愛德華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!那是敵人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一部向本空母飛來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它擊落!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料所餘無幾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞過去也不會引起大爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，要出動機動戰士了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鋼彈!鋼彈出現了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.83,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在艦上嗎?用里歐迎戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里歐20部被毀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.15,0:16:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼!把他擊落海裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用坎沙消滅他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.52,0:16:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人的船呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開了本船隊   好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.07,0:16:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有鋼彈從另一部\N運輸機裡出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.74,0:16:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡洋艦上的鋼彈毀了艦橋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里歐部隊70%被毀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾亞利玆不能出擊嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!所有升降機被擊毀了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.12,0:16:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂‧安特校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒法停止艦上鋼彈的攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過!把他擊落海裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用逐一向我報告情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我指示做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.40,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈在起飛彈射器前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.14,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!用彈射器\N把里歐發射出去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎?   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝上這個高機動推進器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能像艾亞利玆般活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能飛到另一部鋼彈那裡就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想攻擊特列斯大人的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.85,0:17:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妄想!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現目標，殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別得意忘形，鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不能阻止我!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你令我這麼棘手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但到此為止了!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.23,0:19:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾開!夠了吧，妳贏不了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到鋼彈的威力這麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.84,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的上司想和我打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.15,0:19:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我就在這裡收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.15,0:19:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人!\N危險!請你離開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後的交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯?是真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.23,0:20:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛快的一戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你現在不在這裡殺死我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少次我也會來殺你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望和你再戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.26,0:21:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人，你為何放走他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.33,0:21:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是機動戰士的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.80,0:21:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得可以再給他一次機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開機動戰士和我決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很有男子氣概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.61,0:21:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定要讓他用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他擅長的機動戰士和我決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.70,0:22:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他…成功了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.23,0:22:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，不用回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.15,0:22:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.26,0:22:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.26,0:22:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.26,0:22:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.26,0:22:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.76,0:22:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.26,0:23:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.76,0:23:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.26,0:23:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.26,0:23:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.26,0:23:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球圈統一聯合崩潰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.39,0:23:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界踏上混亂之途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.03,0:23:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛和迪歐繼續抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.53,0:23:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪魁禍首的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.00,0:23:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面，傑克斯為了奪回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.77,0:23:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匹斯克拉福特的故鄉山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.67,0:23:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他駕駛托爾吉斯出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.67,0:23:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，托爾吉斯是部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.41,0:23:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過於危險的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.21,0:23:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新機動戰記鋼彈W，第九話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.75,0:23:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亡國的肖像
